Detailed Description

cvmx_usbc::_grxstspd

Receive Status Debug Read Register, Device Mode (GRXSTSPD)

A read to the Receive Status Read and Pop register returns and additionally pops the top data entry out of the RxFIFO. This Description is only valid when the core is in Device Mode. For Host Mode use USBC_GRXSTSPH instead. NOTE: GRXSTSPH and GRXSTSPD are physically the same register and share the same offset in the O2P USB core. The offset difference shown in this document is for software clarity and is actually ignored by the hardware.
